Package vstore.framework.communication.download.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DownloadedFileReadyEvent
    This event is published, when a requested download is ready.
    DownloadFailedEvent
    This event gets published by the framework if the download for a file failed.
    DownloadProgressEvent
    This event gets published regularly during a file download.
    DownloadStartEvent
    This event gets published when a download for a file starts.
    MetadataDownloadFailedEvent
    Published when the download of metadata has failed.
    MetadataEvent
    This event gets published once a request for metadata is done.
    NewThumbnailEvent
    This event is published when a thumbnail has finished downloding
    ThumbnailDownloadFailedEvent
    This event gets published by the framework if the download of a thumbnail failed.
